<!-- 购物车（设计「购物袋」语言校准）：标题头 + 卡片行(勾选/媒体/名规格价/圆角步进器/删除) + 信任小字 + 悬浮结算 bar。
     业务逻辑全保留：勾选/加减/删除/全选/合计/结算跳转/空态。设计源 CartScreen·402px 画板 ×1.87→rpx。 -->
<view class="ld-cart" wx:if="{{items.length}}">
  <view class="ld-cart-head">
    <view class="ld-cart-title">购物袋</view>
    <view class="ld-cart-sub">挑好的小伙伴都在这儿，随时结算带走</view>
  </view>

  <view class="ld-cart-list">
    <view class="ld-cart-row" wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="index">
      <view class="ld-check {{item.selected ? 'on' : ''}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-sku="{{item.sku}}" bind:tap="onToggle"></view>
      <image wx:if="{{item.cover}}" class="ld-cart-row-img" src="{{item.cover}}" mode="aspectFill" />
      <view wx:else class="ld-cart-row-img"></view>
      <view class="ld-cart-row-mid">
        <view class="ld-cart-row-name">{{item.name}}</view>
        <view class="ld-cart-row-tag" wx:if="{{item.sku}}">{{item.sku}}</view>
        <view class="ld-cart-row-price">
          <text class="ld-cart-was" wx:if="{{item.was}}">¥{{item.was}}</text>
          <text class="ld-cart-now">¥{{item.price}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="ld-cart-row-act">
        <view class="ld-stepper">
          <view class="ld-step {{item.qty <= 1 ? 'dim' : ''}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-sku="{{item.sku}}" data-qty="{{item.qty}}" bind:tap="onDec">−</view>
          <text class="ld-step-qty">{{item.qty}}</text>
          <view class="ld-step" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-sku="{{item.sku}}" data-qty="{{item.qty}}" bind:tap="onInc">+</view>
        </view>
        <view class="ld-cart-row-del" data-id="{{item.id}}" data-sku="{{item.sku}}" bind:tap="onRemove">删除</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="ld-cart-trust">包邮到家 · 七天无理由退货 · 官方正品保障</view>

  <view class="ld-checkbar-space"></view>
  <view class="ld-checkbar {{selectedCount ? '' : 'empty'}}">
    <view class="ld-selectall" bind:tap="onToggleAll">
      <view class="ld-check {{allSelected ? 'on' : ''}}"></view>
      <text>全选</text>
    </view>
    <view class="ld-checkbar-total">
      <text class="ld-checkbar-label">合计</text>
      <text class="ld-checkbar-num">{{totalLabel}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="ld-checkout-btn {{selectedCount ? '' : 'dim'}}" bind:tap="onCheckout">去结算({{selectedCount}})</view>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="ld-cart-empty" wx:else>
  <view class="ld-empty-emoji">🦆</view>
  <view class="ld-empty-title">购物袋还空着</view>
  <view class="ld-empty-hint">去挑一只喜欢的小鸭吧</view>
  <view class="ld-empty-btn" bind:tap="onGoHome">去逛逛</view>
</view>
